                     <interp inst="t17840707-58-off294" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17840707-58-cd295" type="crimeDate">5th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840707-58-off294 t17840707-58-cd295"></join>, one mans saddle, value 4 s. and four pounds weight of iron spike nails, value 6 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17840707-58-victim626" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Trotter
                  <interp inst="t17840707-58-victim626" type="surname" value="Trotter"></interp>
